					<p>RUFORUM Monthly provides information on activities of the Regional Universities Forum for Capacity Building in Agriculture.More information on RUFORUM activities can be accessed on the RUFORUM BLOG at <a href="http://ruforum.wordpress.com" target="_blank">http://ruforum.wordpress.com</a>.</p>
